reviewText: Imaginative stories for kids, from Big Idea that are clean, wacky, and fun.
This is a cute children's video. It has a good lesson presented in an enjoyable fashion for young children. This is one of a series which the young children of our church enjoy.
This movie is also available on dvd but was purchased on VHS because it was a bit cheaper that the dvd prices. 3-2-1 Penguins have biblical messages in them and are very enjoyable even by grownups.
As always, wacky fun with a good message for kids. All of us, from my 5-yr-old to my 8-yr-old boys to the grown-ups enjoy this.
This is a great movie for the whole family! My kids love to watch all the episodes of 321 Penguins!
